      "description": "Clean good-condition example that presents well overall and should make a satisfying driver for someone who wants a nicely kept car without paying mint-condition money. The body, paint, trim, and interior appear well cared for, with the kind of light wear and minor imperfections you would expect from a used vehicle that has been enjoyed but not neglected. It looks complete, usable, and above average overall, though a very particular show-car buyer should still expect some age-related cosmetic flaws and signs of normal use on close inspection. A solid, attractive car that offers strong value and should be a good fit for a buyer seeking a dependable, well-presented example.",
